$$\text{Qs/Qt}=([{\text{PAO}}_{\text{2}}-{\text{PaO}}_{\text{2}}]\times \text{0}.\text{003})/[([{\text{PAO}}_{\text{2}}-{\text{PaO}}_{\text{2}}]\times \text{0}.\text{003})\text{+5}]$$
